        {
            "title": "澳大利亞駐美大使陸克文將提前卸任 早前的批評言論曾惹怒川普",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bJVKZNrekHA9KJvgRT8Clg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ef51d34c7fb309cec5568e3b01619e74\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 澳大利亞駐美國大使<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:陸克文;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/陸克文\">陸克文</a>將比計畫提前一年卸任，他過去對美國總統唐納德·川普的批評招致後者不滿，也因此給他的駐美大使任期蒙上陰影。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">澳大利亞總理<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:阿爾巴尼斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/阿爾巴尼斯\">阿爾巴尼斯</a>周二表示，尚未確定接任者，具體人選將在「適當時候」公佈。陸克文將於3月底離任，出任亞洲協會(Asia Society)全球主席，在紐約和華盛頓兩地辦公。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"陸克文攝影：Aaron Schwartz/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t4CokPHFoALMk0ExUDPnfA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/63ba238b8f61a588e09556d424784cfa\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">陸克文攝影：Aaron Schwartz/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">陸克文的離任正逢澳大利亞尋求擴大與美國在關鍵礦產和貿易方面的合作，而意識形態和政策分歧、以及川普的不可預測性和關稅政策都仍在考驗著兩國關係。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6298414c-7f7e-3256-aca7-eb66ef65e1c1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普2025年重返白宮後，陸克文的駐美大使身份就成為了一個摩擦點，他在2023年出任大使之前發表的公開批評重新引發外界關注，比如2022年2月在社交媒體上發帖稱川普是「西方的叛徒」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿爾巴尼斯與川普10月的首次面對面會晤中，緊張關係公開顯露出來，川普回憶起這些言論，並告訴陸克文：「我不喜歡你，可能永遠也不會。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這次交鋒一度使有關國防和經濟合作的會談黯然失色，迫使阿爾巴尼斯不得不在陸克文是否勝任這一職位的問題上應對批評和質疑。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2024年入主白宮之前， 川普曾說陸克文不是個聰明人，並警告說，如果他對川普新一屆政府「抱有敵意」，那就不太可能繼續待在這個位子上。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Australia’s US Envoy to Step Down Early After Trump Friction</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E%E9%A7%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E9%99%B8%E5%85%8B%E6%96%87%E5%B0%87%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D%E5%8D%B8%E4%BB%BB-%E6%97%A9%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E6%9B%BE%E6%83%B9%E6%80%92%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE-094912320.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-13 18:56:07",
