            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "印度和中國尋求重建軍事互信 維持邊境和平",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 印度最資深的陸軍軍官表示，中印兩國最高領導層希望維持邊境和平，並致力於彌合兩國軍隊間的信任缺口。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">印度陸軍參謀長Upendra Dwivedi在新德里對記者表示，「我們正在努力增強兩國軍隊間的互信。包括總理、國防和外交部長在內的最高領導層近幾個月已舉行會晤」，軍隊內部對保持邊境和平存在緊迫感。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位軍事將領的表態強化了政治領袖修復雙邊關係的努力。2020年6月，兩國發生數十年最嚴重邊境衝突，造成多名士兵死亡，兩國關係一度跌至冰點。雙方已同意從剩餘摩擦點將部隊後撤，為印度總理納倫德拉·莫迪去年八月訪華鋪平了道路，這是他七年來首次訪華。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-90474561-71fe-393c-a4f3-fe1f4ae1d79b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在最近與中方官員的會談中，印度方面將沿著這條長達3,488公里、存在爭議的喜馬拉雅邊境實現和平與穩定，作為推動雙邊關係正常化努力的核心內容。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題India, China Seek to Rebuild Military Trust to Keep Border Calm</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
